assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa78fdadbf047f6a086aadde7801886d286a875b","tid":138791,"uid":32309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"令人記你一世有好多方法<br />\n一係好出名 希特拉咁<br />\n一係就睇你點理解一世兩個字<br />\n你一世係佢身邊咁 佢都係記你一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582f6454366a0ff059720809d623f4e96d2ad420","tid":138791,"uid":37993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}